To compile the code please use the make file.
The make file supports both compile as well as clean functionality

Compile:
make

Clean:
make clean

To execute the code use the following command:
hexdump : 
hw1 hexdump <filename>

enc-base64:
hw1 enc-base64 <filename>

dec-base64:
hw1 dec-base64 <filename>